<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:125%;"><strong>SCPF Project Proposal</strong></span></p>
</div>
<br />
<strong>FROM:</strong> Dr. Judith Low<br />
<strong>TO:</strong> Overwatch Command<br />
<strong>DATE:</strong> November 09, 2019<br />
<strong>RE:</strong> The Kelipat Nogah Initiative.
<hr />
<p>The threat represented by the growing strength of the Sarkic cults cannot be underestimated. While long thought to have been rendered ineffectual by their long persecution at the hands of the Church of the Broken God, it has become clear in recent months that the Sarkic Cults are not as toothless as once believed.</p>
<p>While we have known for quite some time that the Sarkic cults represent the remnants of a once-unified and powerful state, we were mistaken in believing that they were ever truly defeated. The conflict that we now call the War of the Flesh was devastating in both its reach and impact. We now estimate that that conflict alone was responsible for the deaths of upwards of 30 million people, and was the likely cause of the Bronze Age Collapse.</p>
<p>This war represented one of the single most catastrophic events in human history and had the net effect of drastically reducing the population in a way that we have yet to fully comprehend. Whole genetic lineages that may have represented entirely different branches of <em>homo sapiens</em> were wiped off the planet in a mere handful of years.</p>
<p>The impact of this conflict cannot be understated, as a modern equivalent would be nothing less of global nuclear war.</p>
<p>It should be noted that if the Sarkics were ever able to attain the level of sophistication and organization that gave rise to the Kalmaktama Empire, the world as we know it would be forever changed. Let us not kid ourselves, the Foundation and other international organizations are not ready to face a threat of this magnitude, and if such a threat truly does exist, they have had millennia to plan and prepare for every possible response.</p>
<p>My proposal is simple. The apparatus of the Foundation is already in place throughout the world to begin moving against the Sarkic cults that we know about. Up until this point, we have been mostly content to let sleeping dogs lie, but I believe the time has come to dramatically increase our efforts in containing the Sarkic contagion. We are finding more and more offshoots of the Sarkic tree every day, and many of the groups we are locating have already had centuries to set down deep roots.</p>
<p>Project Sitra Achra was a good test bed for how well the Foundation can interact with elements of both the <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/church-of-the-broken-god-hub">Church of the Broken God</a> and the <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/goc-hub-page">Global Occult Coalition</a>. Those surviving Project personnel could be easily reassigned to the Initiative and would serve as an experienced veteran core, one that would provide excellent resources in training and outfitting a full-scale Initiative such as this.</p>
<p>We know the threat, now we must act on it.</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p>- Dr. Judith Low<br />
<em>Department of History - Religious GoI Threat Analysis.</em></p>
</div>
