<div class="title-style">
<h6 id="toc0"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Xi-8 (&quot;The Last To Fall&quot;)</strong></span></span></h6>
</div>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.scp-wiki.net/local--files/the-graveyard/xi-8.png" width="300px" alt="xi-8.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div style="border:solid 1px #000000; color:#000000; border-radius: 10px; background:#c9c9c9; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding:10px">
<p><strong>MTF Designation:</strong> Xi-8<br />
<strong>Callsign:</strong> The Last to Fall<br />
<strong>Primary Specialty:</strong> Acquisition and/or termination of Sarkic entities and artifacts<br />
<strong>Command:</strong> Commander Malachai ben Liraz</p>
<p><strong>Overview:</strong> <em>Made up by a core group of Project: Sitra Achra personnel, Xi-8 is uniquely suited to external threats posed by the Sarkic Cults. Each member of this MTF has undergone extensive training in counter-occult initiatives, and is well-versed in Sarkic history.</em></p>
<hr />
<h3 id="toc1"><span><strong>Unit Listing:</strong></span></h3>
<h5 id="toc2"><span>Alpha Company</span></h5>
<p><strong>Command:</strong> Commander Malachai ben Liraz<br />
<strong>Organization:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>1 Headquarters Element, with 23 assigned personnel.</li>
<li>1st Platoon: Infiltration - 12 members (6 Active, 6 support/reserve)</li>
<li>2nd Platoon: Expedition - 16 members (8 active, 8 support/reserve)</li>
<li>3rd Platoon: Heavy Weapons - 22 members (Two 5-person fire teams, 12 support/reserve)</li>
<li>4th Platoon: Paraspecialist - 18 members (8 active, 10 support)</li>
</ul>
<h5 id="toc3"><span>Beta Company</span></h5>
<p><strong>Command:</strong> Lt. Commander Eleanore Montpelier<br />
<strong>Orginzation:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Shares HQ Element with First Company</li>
<li>1st Platoon: Transport - 14 members (Two 4-person vehicle teams w/vehicles, 6 support)</li>
<li>2nd Platoon: Hive Breach - 26 members (12 active, 14 support)</li>
<li>3rd Platoon: Event Suppression - 26 members (14 active, 10 support)</li>
<li>4th Platoon: Air Support - 18 members (6 pilots with combat troop helicopters, 12 support)</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p><strong>Effectiveness Projection:</strong> <em>With the inclusion of Paraspecialists provided by the GOC and the CotBG, Xi-8 should now be able to handle most, if not all mid-level Sarkic Infestations. While not yet the ideal as laid out by Dr. Low, this is a good first step.</em></p>
</div>
